divs: Sighting DetailsI told the dispatcher was looked liked a landing light that was way to low made a high speed turn to the north then you could see about 8 to 10 in a tight formation. kept going north till out of sight. the news the next day said it was self propelled space junk. BS!
Summary: was on patroll looked to west big bright light moving east
